@node "Impo" "Important!"
A header file will be shown if it exists in the  doors  directory
as  'title.txt'.  The  cookie output exists as 'liners.cfg' - but
there must be NO empty lines in the cookie file.

Needs: rexxtricks.library
       rexxsupport.library
